"title": "7120: Christians",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7120",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those who belong to Jesus Christ; other designations in Scripture are believers, disciples and the children of God. Originally a nickname, the term is only used three times in the Bible.</p>\n<h2>The use of the term</h2>\n<h3>Disciples first called Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:26\">ACT 11:26</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Agrippa not persuaded</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:28\">ACT 26:28</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Suffering as a Christian</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:16\">1PE 4:16</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Other biblical designations of Christians</h2>\n<h3>Christians described as believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44\">ACT 2:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32\">ACT 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12\">ACT 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1\">JAS 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as brothers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:11\">HEB 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:3\">ACT 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:2\">COL 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:10\">REV 19:10</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19\">MAT 28:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">ACT 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:7\">ACT 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:52\">ACT 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as children of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12\">JHN 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:21\">ROM 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:26-Gal4:7\">GAL 3:26–4:7</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5\">ACT 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:11\">ACT 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1\">ACT 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:3\">ACT 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:5\">ROM 16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:1\">2CO 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">COL 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">COL 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:15\">1TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as the elect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1\">1PE 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:22\">MAT 24:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:7\">ROM 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:10\">2TI 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:1\">TIT 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as heirs of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:29\">GAL 3:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:7\">GAL 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:6\">EPH 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as members of God's household</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19\">EPH 2:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:15\">1TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as the people of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:10\">1PE 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19\">EPH 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3\">REV 21:3</a></p>\n<h3>Christians described as saints</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:7\">ROM 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:25\">ROM 15:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:2\">1CO 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:1\">2CO 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:13\">2CO 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:15\">EPH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></p>",
